      ],
      "paragraphs": [
        "Folio3 is a proud Direct (Tier 1) Microsoft Cloud Solution Provider (CSP) offering a comprehensve suite of cloud and business applications licensing solutions, value-added services, and unparalleled support to businesses of all sizes.",
        "Through Microsoft CSP, Folio3 offers flexible licensing plans (monthly, quarterly, annually) with no locking period or upfront cost. You pay only for what you need. We’re not just solution providers, we are your trusted advisors to drive strategy, deployment, and business success."
      ],
