    {
      "headings": [
        {
          "tag": "h2",
          "text": "Why Partner with Folio3 as your Microsoft Cloud Solution Provider"
        },
        {
          "tag": "h3",
          "text": "One-stop-shop"
        },
        {
          "tag": "h3",
          "text": "Flexible Payment Plans"
        },
        {
          "tag": "h3",
          "text": "Better Pricing Guaranteed"
        },
        {
          "tag": "h3",
          "text": "Your Trusted Advisor"
        },
        {
          "tag": "h3",
          "text": "24/7 Ongoing Support"
        },
        {
          "tag": "h3",
          "text": "Microsoft Expertise"
        }
      ],
      "paragraphs": [
        "Your Success is our Priority",
        "Your single point of contact for all cloud services and business applications, simplifying your tech management and ecosystem",
        "Access cloud & business app licenses without upfront costs. Choose monthly or annual billing, with the option to adjust fees based on actual usage.",
        "Gain access to competitive pricing compared to traditional options without worrying about implementation cost and consumption lifecycles.",
        "Your trusted technology advisor to guide you in selecting the right services and applications to optimize your technology investments.",
        "From initial setup to ongoing maintenance and troubleshooting, get access to top-notch technical support and a range of services.",
        "Improve your IT efficiency with a esteemed Tier-1 Microsoft Solution Designation Partner who is also a Global Cloud Solution Provider in more than 8 Regions Across the Globe."
      ],
